Inference¶

In [29]:
results = []
dataToPlot = []
for i in range(1,462):
    paths = f"/Users/maheshsaravanan/Documents/HemoScan/Dataset/{i:04d}"
    out,data = inference1(model = model_obj, path = paths,transform = data2validate.dataset.dataset.transform, mean = hb_mean, std = hb_std,Print = False)
    results.append((out))
    dataToPlot.append(data)
results = np.array(results).reshape(len(results),2)
